{"tid":1588892,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"924全港逆權公民放映會","createTime":"2019-09-23T04:34:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T02:26:37.000Z","uid":237057,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"181a72212f0ae005c113db06db841ebef90895ee","tid":1588892,"uid":237057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:34:42.000Z","msg":"「🚨大件事啦❗️全港性活動終於連結最藍地區-油塘啦‼️‼️‼️🚨」<br />\n<br />\n老老實實，大家都知油塘出哂名多廢老又多休班狗，平時有咩活動想搞都特別難，今次終於有班油塘巴絲響應全港活動，企出黎搞場逆權公民放映會，唔係唔黎支持下呀嘛！（加啲連登emoji）<br />\n<br />\n油塘逆權公民放映會💬<br />\n日期：9月24日（星期二）<br />\n時間： 8:00pm-10:30pm<br />\n地點：油塘地鐵站B出口<br />\n<br />\n⚠️希望咁多唔同區嘅手足黎撐下場，全港十八區最難搞非油塘莫屬，你地嘅支持真心可以令成班油塘手足知道，唔係藍絲休班狗多就乜撚嘢都搞唔起！！⚠️（加啲連登emoji）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qe5nLSv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqe5nLSv.jpg&h=1a4c7106&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T2z4eLW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT2z4eLW.jpg&h=0a793cc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WrmBQjr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWrmBQjr.jpg&h=84e7a123&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Bzf5TM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Bzf5TM.jpg&h=be9b24ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n👏🏻多謝大家👏🏻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命❗️<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hk